    "visualHierarchy": "The hero image establishes prominence, followed by the product title (largest text), price, seller info, and then the CTA button.  Size and color contrast enhance the hierarchy.",
    "variantSelectionRationale": "For the button, I selected the `Size: Large`, `Type: Filled`, and `Color: Green` variants to create prominence.  The large size emphasizes the CTA, the filled style is clear and unambiguous, and green is associated with action and positivity in the design system. Other size variants would be less visible, and outlined or text styles are less impactful for a conversion-oriented CTA.",
    "nativeElementJustification": "With moment significance of 0.7 and emotional intent including \"impress\", this product detail screen warrants enhanced treatment.  A native rectangle with a subtle gradient background adds visual appeal while maintaining the functional components. This creates a balance between aesthetics and efficient interaction."
  }
}
